mainInformation.origin: You can find information about the origin on the packaging in the store.

petFoodBasicInformation.composition: Composition: Meat and animal derivatives (38% of which 14% of Chicken*), Cereals, Vegetable protein extracts, Oils and fats, minerals, Various sugars, Yeasts, Derivatives of vegetable origin (0.1% dehydrated catnip).*Chicken is number one ingredient.
petFoodBasicInformation.additives: Additives: Nutritional additives: IU/kg: Vit A: 32000; Vit D3: 1040; Vit E: 170;  mg/kg: Iron (II) sulphate monohydrate: (Fe:86); Calcium iodate anhydrous: (I:2.2); Copper (II) sulphate pentahydrate: (Cu:13); Manganous sulphate monohydrate: (Mn:40); Zinc sulphate monohydrate: (Zn:130); Sodium selenite: (Se:0.12). antioxidants.

petFoodStorageInformation.instructions: Feeding guide: Designed to be recyclable *Daily feeding amount up to:Adult 4kg      14g or approx. 34 piecesClean, fresh drinking water should always be available.For your cat’s health, respect the feeding guide and adjust the main meal accordingly.Supervise your cat when giving him/her the treat.
